sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SRE
    participant OC as oc CLI
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Pod as must-gather Pod<br/>(gather.sh)
    participant Scripts as Component Gather Scripts<br/>(13 parallel processes)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>$DST_DIR
    participant Copy as Copy Container<br/>(tar stream)

    Note over User,Copy: Flow 1: OpenShift Must-Gather (oc adm must-gather)

    User->>OC: oc adm must-gather --image=must-gather:tag
    OC->>API: Create must-gather Pod<br/>Auth: User kubeconfig
    API->>Pod: Schedule Pod<br/>SA: cluster-admin (temp binding)

    Pod->>Pod: detect_k8s_distro()<br/>→ OpenShift detected

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Pod,API: Platform-Level Collection
        Pod->>API: oc adm inspect ns/redhat-ods-operator<br/>Auth: SA token (cluster-admin)
        API-->>Pod: Operator pods, logs, deployments
        Pod->>API: oc get DSCInitialization, DataScienceCluster<br/>Auth: SA token
        API-->>Pod: Platform CRs (YAML)
        Pod->>FS: Write YAML + logs
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Pod,FS: Parallel Component Collection (13 scripts)
        Pod->>Scripts: fork 13 background processes
        par gather_serving.sh
            Scripts->>API: oc adm inspect InferenceService,<br/>ServingRuntime, AuthConfig...<br/>Auth: SA token
            API-->>Scripts: KServe resources
        and gather_data_science_pipelines.sh
            Scripts->>API: oc adm inspect DSPA, Workflow...<br/>Auth: SA token
            API-->>Scripts: Pipeline resources
        and gather_notebooks.sh
            Scripts->>API: oc adm inspect Notebook,<br/>ImageStream...<br/>Auth: SA token
            API-->>Scripts: Workbench resources
        and gather_kuberay.sh + 9 others
            Scripts->>API: oc adm inspect component CRs<br/>Auth: SA token
            API-->>Scripts: Component resources
        end
        Scripts->>FS: Write YAML + logs per component
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Pod,FS: Cluster-Scoped Collection
        Pod->>API: oc get nodes, api-resources<br/>Auth: SA token
        API-->>Pod: Cluster state
        Pod->>FS: Write cluster info
    end

    Pod->>Copy: tar stream of $DST_DIR
    Copy-->>OC: Transfer collected data
    OC-->>User: must-gather archive (.tar.gz)

    Note over User,Copy: Flow 2: xKS Must-Gather (Kubernetes Job)

    User->>API: kubectl apply -f must-gather-job.yaml<br/>Auth: User kubeconfig
    API->>Pod: Schedule Job Pod<br/>SA: must-gather-sa (read-only)

    Pod->>Pod: detect_k8s_distro()<br/>→ AKS/EKS/CKS detected

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Pod,API: kubectl_inspect Collection (xKS mode)
        Pod->>API: kubectl api-resources --namespaced<br/>Auth: SA token (read-only)
        API-->>Pod: Available API resources
        Pod->>API: kubectl get <resources> -o yaml<br/>Auth: SA token
        API-->>Pod: Resource YAML
        Pod->>API: kubectl logs <pods> --all-containers<br/>Auth: SA token
        API-->>Pod: Pod logs (current + previous)
        Pod->>FS: Write YAML + logs
    end

    User->>API: kubectl cp must-gather-pod:/tmp/must-gather ./output<br/>Auth: User kubeconfig (TLS 1.2+)
    API-->>User: Collected diagnostic data
